{"thag2.14:0.1":"Theragatha 2.14 ","thag2.14:0.2":"Dukanipata ","thag2.14:0.3":"Dutiyavagga ","thag2.14:0.4":"Somamittattheragatha ","thag2.14:1.1":"“Parittam darumaruyha, ","thag2.14:1.2":"yatha side mahannave; ","thag2.14:1.3":"Evam kusitamagamma, ","thag2.14:1.4":"sadhujivipi sidati; ","thag2.14:1.5":"Tasma tam parivajjeyya, ","thag2.14:1.6":"kusitam hinaviriyam. ","thag2.14:2.1":"Pavivittehi ariyehi, ","thag2.14:2.2":"pahitattehi jhayibhi; ","thag2.14:2.3":"Niccam araddhaviriyehi, ","thag2.14:2.4":"panditehi sahavase”ti. ","thag2.14:2.5":"… Somamitto thero …. "}